{"tid":453082,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲熟悉飛機","createTime":"2017-10-31T01:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T04:15:33.000Z","uid":99805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"52458a573da8717440ee66953099cc6e1d96d013","tid":453082,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T01:06:08.000Z","msg":"今朝坐架因航....果對機翼上下搖晃得好勁.....<br />\n好似就斷咁,同埋架機不時有好多金屬扭曲聲<br />\n<br />\n雖然我知好低可能空中解體,但有無巴打解釋下咩事<br />\n同埋點解機翼搖到咁都無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c33152040dc4211198659b6ace9efabe588bc9c","tid":453082,"uid":36434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T01:07:45.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"f575bf3d39ef517477897be243ded54810741d9e","tid":453082,"uid":36434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T01:07:57.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"ab9e4e6049ac6f4bd3994446434133c2efd39724","tid":453082,"uid":36434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T01:08:07.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"9575cd8d374262ea01aeae8de7f0a47a4c685de2","tid":453082,"uid":36434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T01:08:23.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"713c8a22213afb2dc55d8c6f5530f2c24730e670","tid":453082,"uid":4052,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T01:10:04.000Z","msg":"比較熟打飛機"},{"pid":"709244972d8423d166aa5f659ac2fa468d6190f1","tid":453082,"uid":3724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T01:10:28.000Z","msg":"我見過幅圖，787對翼係可以屈到好高<br />\n但你嗰架應該唔係787"},{"pid":"a4de3ea3c91ec6c4240687773b8fdbc1ac320c6b","tid":453082,"uid":94909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T01:11:26.000Z","msg":"機翼既設計係容許佢上下郁 吸收外在既壓力 等佢冇咁易收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c500d088ff0b9890fa120834e7d00cdbf98f017","tid":453082,"uid":39393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T01:12:34.000Z","msg":"對翼本身就好有彈性去reduce stress<br />\n設計上係可以bend好大角度<br />\n如果冇得上下彈太大stress就會直接斷<br />\n下面條片係對翼既flex test<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ai2HmvAXcU0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAi2HmvAXcU0&d=en1O0unu1ryP%2FPqfndsG5E%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=78bb7111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ai2HmvAXcU0</a>"},{"pid":"cb5bd0d9a26222954b191b6032238bf0f365f7fd","tid":453082,"uid":146976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T01:14:36.000Z","msg":"簡單咁講：因為機翼設計係越硬越固定既話就越易折斷，反而機翼因為flexible咗抗衡到力先冇咁易折斷。<br />\n利申：非專業性解釋"},{"pid":"362e99400429ac6a69e3561526063bcb1ef82838","tid":453082,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T01:24:47.000Z","msg":"其實飛機引擎都係靠幾點固定著<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以唔駛咁擔心機翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d2fc28cf55a433820991e8e42aa93125af6c1cd","tid":453082,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:51:19.000Z","msg":"小弟坐過不下100次飛機<br />\n但每次都好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為覺得空難得就99%死硬"},{"pid":"5911f9cb3605900921275875d1ca36f0043f6a46","tid":453082,"uid":5858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:00:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟坐過不下100次飛機<br />\n但每次都好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為覺得空難得就99%死硬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你放心 你行行下街俾天跌落黎嘅隕石撞死都仲高機率過遇到空難"},{"pid":"699615f81550e3f983aa4ed3d74f447c79a4ebb6","tid":453082,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:03:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小弟坐過不下100次飛機<br />\n但每次都好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為覺得空難得就99%死硬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你放心 你行行下街俾天跌落黎嘅隕石撞死都仲高機率過遇到空難</blockquote><br />\n咁緊係知啦,個意思係等如你最信任既人話比你聽,依加彌敦道無車,綠燈,叫你合埋眼過都係淆既道理一樣"},{"pid":"2af2444037f15641796169fbe17f1e10131dd113","tid":453082,"uid":9050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:07:34.000Z","msg":"氣流好平常 有彈性先係正常<br />\n如果比你知道 個引擎得幾支野shot住個翼 可能你仲驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：H記維修員"},{"pid":"a22e9d804a4872f5f612fe8907fe7b32219249ae","tid":453082,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:10:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>氣流好平常 有彈性先係正常<br />\n如果比你知道 個引擎得幾支野shot住個翼 可能你仲驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：H記維修員</blockquote><br />\n眼不見為乾淨<br />\n去餐廳食野都唔會諗個廚R完袋有無洗手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁巴打請教下,點解成日有D金屬壓迫聲<br />\n又話者有咩情況下係唔安全既警號?(唔計著火)"},{"pid":"4d171af62a83032327fa4ce0195515994f691c3b","tid":453082,"uid":146976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/01/121531_a08cc2734efe6f821b2d347359f163a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F01%2F121531_a08cc2734efe6f821b2d347359f163a4.jpg&h=bb640c2f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}